---
canvas: 640x360
bg: #0f172a
fps: 30
---

# Spotlight Reveal - demonstrates circle mask with animation

rect background w:640 h:360 fill:#1e293b | 0s - 5s
  x: 320
  y: 180

text secret "WELCOME" font:Roboto size:72 fill:#e74c5c weight:bold | 0s - 5s
  x: 320
  y: 180
  mask: circle(320, 180, 80)

text hint "Moving spotlight reveals text" font:Roboto size:14 fill:#64748b | 0s - 5s
  x: 320
  y: 320
